    title: "How XGBoost + Prophet Beat Manual Forecasting by 3× in Retail",
    excerpt: "A 120-store UK retail chain reduced demand forecast error from 27% to 8.3% MAPE, cut excess inventory by 34%, and eliminated stockouts on top SKUs by 63% — using a hybrid XGBoost + Prophet ML pipeline.",
    author: "Oleksiy Kovalenko",
    category: "AI та Автоматизація",
    tags: ["Machine Learning", "Demand Forecasting", "Retail", "XGBoost", "Prophet", "Inventory Optimisation", "Supply Chain", "UK Retail"],
    date: "2026-05-02",
    readTime: 9,
    emoji: "📦",
    color: "from-blue-600 to-indigo-800",
