    title: "Predicting Equipment Failure Before It Happens with ML",
    excerpt: "A practical guide to building predictive maintenance systems that reduce unplanned downtime by 73% using sensor data, time-series ML models, and edge inference.",
    author: "Oleksiy Kovalenko",
    category: "AI та Автоматизація",
    tags: ["ML", "Predictive Maintenance", "Manufacturing", "IoT", "Time Series"],
    date: "2026-05-02",
